Detailed Description

Configure priority of ISS data sources. Refer IOCTL VPS_ISS_SET_ISS_STREAM_PRI_CONFIG.

Warning
All combinations of streams/priority may not be supported. Please refer TRM for valid combinations.

Field Documentation

uint32_t vpsissRoutingConfig::cportId[VPS_ISS_INIT_MAX]

Applicable only for CAL. Ignored for others. Currently ignored, capture core configure each of the streams as highest priority.

Number of streams that you want to configure
